import '../style/Nomers.css'
import React from 'react'
import Rules from '../components/rules'
import Nomer1 from '../components/nomer1'
import Nomer2 from '../components/nomer2'
import Nomer3 from '../components/nomer3'
import Nomer4 from '../components/nomer4'
import Nomer5 from '../components/nomer5'
import Nomer6 from '../components/nomer6'

function NomersPage() {
	return (
		<>
			<Rules />
			<Nomer1 />
			<Nomer2 />
			<Nomer3 />
			<Nomer4 />
			<Nomer5 />
			<Nomer6 />
		</>
	)
}

export default NomersPage
